ANACONDA SETUP
Introduction
1) Anaconda is a distribution of python and R programming language that aims to specify package management and deployment in data science and machine learning applications.

2) It was created by Anaconda,Inc.(formerly Known as Continuum Analytics).

How to install it?
Link-https://www.anaconda.com/download/success

Why we use Anaconda?
1)Simplified Package Management
2)Comprehensive Distribution
3)Environment  Management
4)Cross-Platform Compactibility
5)Open-Sourse Tools
6)Community Support
7)Enterprise-Ready
8)Ease of Use

Environment in Anaconda

What is an Environment?
-specific collection of conda packages not only python and R.

Why Use Environments?
*isolated Project
*Maintain Multiple Version
*Reproducibility
